snippet.title: Nazo Puyo (なぞぷよ) for PC-98 | Year 1 Rerun
snippet.description:
To start things off, I am restarting this whole playthrough. I did a terrible job translating and it was a waste of my time. The new videos will be broken down by year, no cutscenes skipped, and recorded in better quality.

Timestamps:
Intro - 0:00
Skeleton-T (Levels 1-10) - 0:42
Draco Centauros (Levels 11-20) - 3:07
Sasoriman (Levels 21-30) - 6:15

#PuyoPuyo #PC98 #NazoPuyo
